  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dead body recovery from container box",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said that a dead body was recovered yesterday morning from a garden in Kavayankulam area of \u200b\u200bPuttalam - Mahakumbukkadawala.",
        "The Mahakumbukkadawala police said that the dead body was recovered from a container box in a 33-acre mango tree plantation in the said area.",
        "A 56-year-old man from Mahava area, who worked in the said mango plantation, has been recovered as a dead body.",
        "Based on a tip-off that a dead body was found inside a container box of the garden, the police went to the spot and started investigations.",
        "According to the police, it has been revealed in the preliminary investigation that the three working in the said mango garden had been drinking alcohol inside the said container box last night and after that there was a heated argument between them.",
        "The police have also said that they suspect that one of the three may have been beaten to death after an argument between the three.",
        "In addition, two others who were reported to have consumed alcohol last night along with the person whose body was recovered have been arrested on suspicion.",
        "The body of the deceased has been kept in the Puttalam Tala Hospital mortuary for post-mortem after the post-mortem.",
        "In connection with this incident, the crime branch is conducting further investigation under the leadership of Police Inspector Kumara, the officer-in-charge of Mahakumbukkadawala police station, in collaboration with the police forensics department."
      ],
